" class=\"ico-feedback\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg><span class=\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">Sept 21, 2024</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent wide\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104pdt1665702711976.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/pdt1665702711976.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/pdt1665702711976.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"pdt1665702711976\" role=\"article\">\n<h1 class=\"title topictitle1\" id=\"ariaid-title1\">\n      Width\n </h1>\n<div class=\"body refbody\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">The line width (where Uniface should wrap text) of a multiline Unifield.\n </p>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"pdt1665702711976__section_w0ab1b5b1_w1ab1b5_w2ab1\">\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"2\" id=\"pdt1665702711976__table_d698e1_d699e1_d700e1\"><caption></caption><colgroup><col/><col/></colgroup><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<p class=\"p\">Technical Name:</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n                           \n                                         LINEWIDTH</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<p class=\"p\">Expected Value:</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<p class=\"p\">Numeric, up to 8 digits</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<p class=\"p\">Default Value:</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">240</code>\n</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"pdt1665702711976__section_mzv_st3_5cc\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d403964e117\">Description</h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"pdt1665702711976__p_d7664e1_d7665e1_d7666e1\">The default width is 240 if one or more of the following\n            conditions is true:</p>\n<ul class=\"ul\" id=\"pdt1665702711976__ul_chv_tt3_5cc\">\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"pdt1665702711976__li_d3701e1_d3702e1_d3703e1\">The field is variable-length. </li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"pdt1665702711976__li_d3704e1_d3705e1_d3706e1\">The field length is greater than 240 bytes. </li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"pdt1665702711976__li_d3707e1_d3708e1_d3709e1\">The field is drawn on the component with a vertical\n               size of two lines or more. </li>\n</ul>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"pdt1665702711976__section_k4j_5t3_5cc\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d403964e138\">Applies to</h2>\n<ul class=\"ul\" id=\"pdt1665702711976__ul_kky_vt3_5cc\">\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"pdt1665702711976__li_d3710e1_d3711e1_d3712e1\"><a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"lpv1665702557117.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/lpv1665702557117.html\" title=\"Property that specifies how the field's data is formatted for display. The value can be a comma-separated list of shorthand codes, or a reference to a modeled field layout.\">Field Layout</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"pdt1665702711976__li_d3713e1_d3714e1_d3715e1\"><a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"ijx1665702711766.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/ijx1665702711766.html\" title=\"A Modeled Field Layout is a Development Object that defines the way data is displayed.\">Modeled Field Layout</a>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2530882\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2530882\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "Width Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Sept 21, 2024 Summarize Uniface 10.4 Width The line width (where Uniface should wrap text) of a multiline Unifield. Technical Name: LINEWIDTH Expected Value: Numeric, up to 8 digits Default Value: 240 Description The default width is 240 if one or more of the following conditions is true: The field is variable-length. The field length is greater than 240 bytes. The field is drawn on the component with a vertical size of two lines or more. Applies to Field Layout Modeled Field Layout Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}